      <title outputclass="H4ForH3_1_9" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">9.104-1</ph> General standards.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p otherprops="Body" outputclass="Body" class="- topic/p ">To be determined responsible, a prospective contractor must-</p>
         <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d530e16">
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d538e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  Have adequate financial resources to perform the contract, or the ability to obtain them (see <xref href="FAR-i1116122.dita#i1116122"
                        base="i1116122"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.104-3</xref>(a));</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d538e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  Be able to comply with the required or proposed delivery or performance schedule, taking into consideration all existing commercial and governmental business commitments;</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d538e41" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  Have a satisfactory performance record (see <xref href="FAR-i1116122.dita#i1116122"
                        base="i1116122"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.104-3</xref>(b) and <xref href="FAR-i1074222.dita#i1074222"
                        base="i1074222"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart 42.15</xref>). A prospective contractor shall not be determined responsible or nonresponsible solely on the basis of a lack of relevant performance history, except as provided in <xref href="FAR-i1116115.dita#i1116115"
                        base="i1116115"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.104-2</xref>;</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d538e59" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  Have a satisfactory record of integrity and business ethics (for example, see <xref href="FAR-i1074222.dita#i1074222"
                        base="i1074222"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart 42.15</xref>).</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d538e71" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  Have the necessary organization, experience, accounting and operational controls, and technical skills, or the ability to obtain them (including, as appropriate, such elements as production control procedures, property control systems, quality assurance measures, and safety programs applicable to materials to be produced or services to be performed by the prospective contractor and subcontractors). (See <xref href="FAR-i1116122.dita#i1116122"
                        base="i1116122"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.104-3</xref>(a).)</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d538e84" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  Have the necessary production, construction, and technical equipment and facilities, or the ability to obtain them (see <xref href="FAR-i1116122.dita#i1116122"
                        base="i1116122"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.104-3</xref>(a)); and</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d538e96" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(g)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  Be otherwise qualified and eligible to receive an award under applicable laws and regulations (see also inverted domestic corporation prohibition at <xref href="FAR-i1116397.dita#i1116397"
                        base="i1116397"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.108</xref>).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
